==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pigtail
<hw>Pig"tail`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The tail
of a pig.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Hair Dressing)</fld> <def>A cue, or queue.</def>
<rj><au>J. & H. Smith.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>A kind of twisted chewing tobacco.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The tobacco he usually cheweth, called <qex>pigtail</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Swift.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pigtailed</ent>⟦br⟧
